examples.en: The alchemists tried to turn lead into gold.

examples.en: The alchemists believed that there were four elements.

examples.en: The alchemists were unable to accept the inconvertible nature of elemental metals.
examples.ru: Алхимики были не в состоянии принять необратимую природу элементарных металлов.
